oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sunset "Kit" Carson Fan Club Membership Card
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Carson, Sunset, 1920-1990; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet featuring a Souvenir Membership Card for the Sunset "Kit Carson Fan Club and containing the ten commandments of the Sharpshooter's Code. The membership card contains a photograph of Sunset Carson, and the negatives would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
